The '''Ministry of Education''' ('''MoE''', {{lang-ar|وزارة التربية والتعليم}}) is a government ministry of the [[United Arab Emirates]]. It has its main offices in [[Abu Dhabi]] and [[Dubai]].<ref>"[https://www.moe.gov.ae/English/Pages/ContactInformation.aspx Contact Information]." Ministry of Education (United Arab Emirates). Retrieved on November 15, 2015.</ref>

